<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section style="padding:0 32px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;" class="reveal">
      <div class="section-tag" style="display:inline-block;">How It Works</div>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.025em;margin:12px auto 0;max-width:560px;">Up and running in days, not months.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-grid reveal">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-title">Connect</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Ecofit sensors attach to your equipment or pull directly from manufacturer consoles via native API integrations. No IT department required. No servers to configure. For most compatible equipment, it's plug-in simple.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-title">Sync</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Data flows automatically to the Ecofit cloud platform. No manual entry, no spreadsheets, no periodic exports. Everything updates in real time — usage events, status changes, error codes, and session data — continuously and automatically.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-title">See</div>
        <div class="step-desc">Usage, status, events, and analytics appear in your Ecofit dashboard within minutes of installation. Your floor comes to life — every asset visible, every session counted, every issue surfaced before your members find it first.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

