        </div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#9ca3af;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;">Universal sensor integration:</div>
        <div class="int-type-brands">
          <span class="int-badge int-badge-gray">Precor</span>
          <span class="int-badge int-badge-gray">Octane</span>
          <span class="int-badge int-badge-gray">True Fitness</span>
