          <span class="int-badge int-badge-gray">CORE Health</span>
          <span class="int-badge int-badge-gray">+ more</span>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:16px;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;">If your equipment isn't listed, our universal sensor likely supports it. Take the assessment to confirm compatibility.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="int-type-card">
        <div class="int-type-icon">🔗</div>
        <div class="int-type-title">Service Platform Linking</div>
        <div class="int-type-desc">Send real-time usage and status data directly to your existing service management platform. When a machine flags an issue, your service team knows immediately — with the full context of usage history and event data already attached to the work order.</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#9ca3af;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;">Available on select platforms:</div>
